Here is a sector that suffers directly and immediately from extended power outages, Domestic Workers. Due to power outages, employers are cutting back on their hours, as the cost of living rises. #eNCA #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Spare a thought for us. This is the plea of domestic workers as they feel the brunt of the energy and economic crises. Some households are either firing them or cutting their hours. The Izwi Domestic Workers Alliance is appealing to homeowners to be more understanding. Watch the video above for more details.